verbose_text: For example, TGFbeta can activate mitogen activated protein kinases (MAPKs), including extracellular signal regulated kinase 1/2 (ERK1/2), p38 MAPK, and c-Jun N-terminal kinases (JNKs), and regulate cell proliferation, migration, and differentiation [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
